title: Christian Dior Medium Lady Dior
description: Christian Dior medium Lady Dior bag in beige lambskin leather with Cannage quilting. Featuring gold-toned hardware, leather top handles & 'DIOR' charms at front. The folding flap closure on top opens to a beige suede interior with zip and patch pockets. Approx dimensions: 24cm(L) x 20cm(H) x 11cm(D), handle drop 10cm & detachable & adjustable strap drop 60cm. Accompanied by Dior card (dated 01/2022), dustbag, box & Lady Dior books. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
